title: Hurricane Joaquin Closures at Cape Lookout National Seashore Advisory #5 (NPS - National Park Service) ...
text: ( Source : NPS - National Park Service ) Date : October 5 , 2015 Contact : BG Horvat , 252-728-2250 ext 3005 Harkers Island, NC - Hurricane Joaquin has moved further East out into the Atlantic Ocean making it less of a threat to Cape Lookout .
